{"id":276,"date":"2017-02-12T09:50:36","date_gmt":"2017-02-12T09:50:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=276"},"modified":"2025-02-11T10:27:14","modified_gmt":"2025-02-11T10:27:14","slug":"dropbox-file-chooser","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/dropbox-file-chooser\/","title":{"rendered":"Dropbox File Chooser"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Currently, the Dropbox file chooser is available for the following features in Perfex CRM:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Tasks<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Invoices<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Estimates<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Proposals<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Leads<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Customer Profile Files<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Contracts<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Project Files<\/strong> \u2013 Supported from version 1.6.0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Setting up Dropbox File Chooser<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To set up the Dropbox file chooser, you will need to create a Dropbox App and obtain a unique App key.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Steps to Create a Dropbox App:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.dropbox.com\/developers\/apps\/create\">Dropbox App Console<\/a>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Create your Dropbox App and retrieve your unique <strong>App Key<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Configuring the App:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have your App Key, follow these steps:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Add your domain where Perfex CRM is installed to the <strong>Chooser domains<\/strong> section of the Dropbox App settings. This ensures the file chooser can work securely.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Copy the <strong>App Key<\/strong> and navigate to <strong>Setup -> Settings -> Misc -> Dropbox App Key<\/strong> in Perfex CRM.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the key and save the settings.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"883\" height=\"824\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-app-key-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-277\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-app-key-1.png 883w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-app-key-1-300x280.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-app-key-1-768x717.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-app-key-1-60x56.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-app-key-1-150x140.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Benefits<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You will now be able to choose files from your Dropbox account without taking up space on your server.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"677\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-button-chooser-768x677.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-278\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-button-chooser-768x677.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-button-chooser-768x677-300x264.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-button-chooser-768x677-60x53.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/dropbox-button-chooser-768x677-150x132.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Using the Dropbox Chooser doesn\u2019t require production approval.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The allowed file types for Dropbox selection follow the settings in <strong>Setup -> Settings -> General -> Allowed file types<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dropbox files cannot be attached to emails (e.g., when sending an invoice to a customer).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a way to convert your PDFs into accessible URLs? Check <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/fixthephoto.com\/convert-pdf-to-url.html\" title=\"Convert PDF to URL tools\">Convert PDF to URL<\/a><\/strong> tools.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Currently, the Dropbox file chooser is available for the following features in Perfex CRM: Setting up Dropbox File Chooser To set up the Dropbox file chooser, you will need to create a Dropbox App and obtain a unique App key. Steps to Create a Dropbox App: Configuring the App: Once you have your App Key, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[31],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-276","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-setup-and-configuration"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/276","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=276"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/276\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=276"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=276"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/